Logs and additional context:
markdown**Operator log immediately after `kubectl delete deployment elasti-resolver`:**
2026-07-02T21:53:15.512Z  INFO  controller/opsInformer.go:102  Public service updated
{"service": "whoami", "es": "demo/whoami"}
2026-07-02T22:34:08.970Z  WARN  controller/opsInformer.go:70   Resolver deployment deleted
